  "_comment_gs1us_mapping": [
    "First Land-Based Receiver CTE per GS1 US 'EPCIS Recommendations for FSMA 204 CTEs' R2.0, §8.",
    "Single ObjectEvent covers the entire CTE when the first land-based receiver assigns the TLC:",
    "  ObjectEvent, action=ADD, bizStep=creating_class_instance, disposition=active.",
    "  readPoint = GLN of the first land-based receiver = TLC source (KDE).",
    "  quantityList.epcClass = newly assigned TLC (GTIN+Batch/Lot).",
    "  eventTime = date the food was landed (KDE).",
    "  ilmd carries seafood-specific KDEs from the GS1 Web Vocabulary:",
    "    - gs1:catchZone (FAO area codes) = locations for the trip during which the food was caught.",
    "    - gs1:harvestDateStart + gs1:harvestDateEnd = harvest date range KDE.",
    "    - gs1:fishType = species / acceptable market name KDE.",
    "  bizTransactionList = reference document type + number KDEs (cert, recadv, po).",
    "NO usfsma: extension fields; all KDEs ride on native EPCIS / GS1 Web Vocabulary fields."
  ],
